Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.89,0:00:02.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:02.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:02.31,0:00:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.31,0:00:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:04.15,0:00:05.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.15,0:00:05.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.61,0:00:07.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:07.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.78,0:00:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.74,0:00:18.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:18.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.58,0:00:20.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:20.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:20.79,0:00:22.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:22.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.54,0:00:24.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:24.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.88,0:00:26.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:26.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.04,0:00:26.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:26.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.67,0:00:36.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:36.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
