Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.12,0:01:02.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于刻画出了火热的激情  那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:01:02.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, I've captured the firey passion that is
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.66,0:01:03.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:03.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,moi
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.21,0:01:10.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么就进来了一只蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:10.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did a clam get in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.88,0:01:19.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒要给你看看玷污我艺术品的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:19.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you for defiling my art
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.93,0:01:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看你干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look what you've done
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.52,0:01:26.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的半身像碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:26.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My bust is busted
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.77,0:01:33.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  有信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:33.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, a message
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.49,0:01:36.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:36.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Hello, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.61,0:01:39.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨面包包寄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:39.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From Sprog-Bub"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,神秘寄信人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A mystery sender
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.96,0:01:48.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:48.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.34,0:01:53.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:53.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Safe travels
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.43,0:01:59.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:01:59.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.39,0:02:03.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:03.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh boy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.35,0:02:04.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星回信了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:04.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick responded
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.77,0:02:10.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点像是鸡鸭互相接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:10.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a duck and a chicken kissing, I think?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上回来  小蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be right back, clammies
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是在试用新款防晒霜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you trying out a new sunscreen?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.32,0:02:21.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:21.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.82,0:02:22.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:22.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是那群死蛤蜊害的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's those stupid clams
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么非得飞过我家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are they flying through my house?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些都是信蛤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're carrier clams
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.75,0:02:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我和派大星在互相飞蛤传书
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick and I are sending each other messages
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.96,0:02:34.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们家的无脑死蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:34.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, your brainless bivalves
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.17,0:02:37.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进了我家窗子  糟蹋了我家艺术品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:37.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are going through my windows and destroying my art
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们向我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just promise me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.18,0:02:41.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞蛤传书别传进我家来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:41.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll stop sending your clams through my window
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看你背后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Behind you"?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们保证
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We promise
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宁静舒适
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:55.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peace and quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是我订的大理石板到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That must be the new marble slabs I ordered
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.24,0:03:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又来几只蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More clams?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绷不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.30,0:03:19.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在得要让我亲爪解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:19.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to take matters into my own tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.09,0:03:27.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能笑章鱼哥社死  不然没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:27.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's rude to laugh at Squidward's hilarious shame
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.52,0:03:34.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我把午饭送过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:34.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I'm sending over lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.07,0:03:37.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都饿坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:37.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm starving
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.79,0:03:52.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你们炖汤愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:52.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have fun at the Chowder Factory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(792,596)}杂烩汤厂
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did it, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.46,0:04:01.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于把那群死蛤蜊赶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:04:01.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You finally put a stop to those stupid clams
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:13.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1398,376)}蛤蜊杂烩汤
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  杂烩汤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:13.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, chowder
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.77,0:04:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你送吃的来  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the grub, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.49,0:04:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们炖汤愉快不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun at the Chowder Factory
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,杂烩汤好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot chowder
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.88,0:04:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打不过就无视好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you can't beat 'em, ignore 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.32,0:05:04.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:04.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidw--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.99,0:05:07.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:07.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白痴大游行过来表演了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The idiot parade is in town
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.83,0:05:11.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:11.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得等五月才能过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't meet until May
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是旧月来着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or was it Septebuary?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.92,0:05:19.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是在让我家信蛤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:19.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just having my carrier clams
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送我去海绵宝宝家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,carry me to SpongeBob's house
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.96,0:05:25.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样去比较轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's easier this way
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.22,0:05:28.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来带你抄近道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:28.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me to show you a shortcut
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:28.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1024,920)}剪
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.02,0:05:41.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旧月再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:41.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you in Septebuary
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么这么久才来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What took you so long?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我路上堵车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ran into traffic
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.03,0:05:49.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还撞了别人家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:49.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And the house
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那群蛤蜊也太爱章鱼哥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those clams sure do love Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像章鱼哥不怎么爱蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not so sure he loves them
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得给蛤蜊训练一下  专门避开他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should train our clams to avoid him
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟别人一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like everybody else does
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1022,590)}蛤蜊点心
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1022,590)}恭喜毕业
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蛤蜊来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here they come
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.30,0:07:28.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:28.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.19,0:07:45.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:45.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我这回穿好了衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least I'm not naked this time
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.99,0:07:57.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在左边  能看到一只光着身子的章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:57.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And on your left, you'll see a naked octopus
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:55.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(374,598)}裤头村观光团
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被反锁在自家门外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,locked out of his house
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.59,0:08:10.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须以火攻火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:10.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have to fight fire with fire
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.22,0:08:19.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:19.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.89,0:08:23.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你在这签名签收包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:23.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sign here to accept the package
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再在这签名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and sign here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.73,0:08:30.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接受伤残以及死亡的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:30.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to accept possibility of injury maiming, or death
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴能认识你  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice knowing you, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.11,0:08:37.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的秘密武器总算到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:37.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally, my secret weapons
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.79,0:08:43.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大扇贝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:43.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A great scallop
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,杀手蛤蜊真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice killer clam
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里有自助餐吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here's a whole buffet
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sic 'em, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.86,0:09:10.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在谁家蛤蜊厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:10.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's got that clam now?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.98,0:09:12.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家扇贝最厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:12.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got the greatest scallop
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.86,0:09:13.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哇  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:13.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wow, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它们好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're so pretty
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.70,0:09:16.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:16.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我买你来是要吓跑那群死蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bought you to scare those dumb clams
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.92,0:09:30.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是跟着一起跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:30.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not dance with them
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Incoming
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.10,0:09:50.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屋主回家一定会气疯的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:50.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, is that guy gonna be mad when he gets home
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全躲不开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:04.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no escaping them
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.25,0:10:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're doomed
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,振作点  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.62,0:10:09.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少我们还有彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:09.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least we have each other
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那种事可让我振作不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That doesn't cheer me up
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.67,0:10:15.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蛤蜊好像都走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:15.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think the clams left
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蛤蜊都没走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The clams didn't leave
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.86,0:10:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许可以等它们全都迁徙完了再出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can just wait 'em out until they migrate?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.32,0:10:38.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:38.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.86,0:10:40.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再等六个月又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:40.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's another six months?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,六个月  六个月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Six months, six months
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.66,0:10:46.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:46.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们貌似在迁徙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we're migrating
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.26,0:11:01.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  执行流星行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:01.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, commence operation Shooting Star
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么  你意思是说要跳窗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What, you mean, like, jump out of the window?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.31,0:11:04.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:04.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.72,0:11:05.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是要跳窗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:05.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jump out the window
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.47,0:11:06.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:06.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跳啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jump, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:17.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jump
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.49,0:11:21.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完蛋  我越飞越远了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:21.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I'm getting farther away
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.28,0:11:25.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  我越飞越远了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:25.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, I'm getting farther away
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我总算远走高飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm finally moving on up
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.13,0:11:42.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是比住海绵宝宝隔壁强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:42.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still better than living next to SpongeBob
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:46.18,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFAF&}过敏来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:47.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(704,368)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:52.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:47.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(718,664)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(644,448)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(772,654)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:50.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(746,532)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:52.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(582,538)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:56.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(484,448)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:56.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(978,578)}千千万万亿
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走过路过都来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come one, come all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:56.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1596,960)}新闻
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别错过我的专业煎炸厨师  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't miss my expert fry cook, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.98,0:12:01.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做出第千千万万亿个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:01.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cookin' his one kazillionth Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,入场费只要五块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Entry fee is only five clams
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是帕奇帕金斯  在蟹堡王现场直播
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perch Perkins here, live at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.66,0:12:14.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于今天这个重大日子为你现场报道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:14.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bringing you the play-by-play on this momentous day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,煎炸厨师登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fry cook of the hour
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝先生  你有何感想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. SquarePants, how do you feel?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不敢相信真的成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it's really happening
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.52,0:12:33.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是我厨师事业中最重要的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:33.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the biggest day of my fry cook career
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来见见今天的幸运顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's meet the lucky customer
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他将会吃到这个非凡的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who gets to eat the marvelous patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.15,0:12:37.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:37.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bas--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.65,0:12:41.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个蟹黄堡肯定平平无奇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:41.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the patty will be mediocre
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.36,0:12:44.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但凡事我都必须争第一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:44.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I must be first at everything
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找点有意义的事做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get a life, people
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才一个蟹黄堡而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.62,0:12:51.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很神啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:51.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it amazing, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.70,0:12:54.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果我是在做第千千万万亿个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:54.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I'm making the kazillionth patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你就接了千千万万亿个点餐单了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then you've written a kazillion orders
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用你提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't remind me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.05,0:13:04.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生  你害海绵宝宝分心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:04.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward, you're distractin' SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我们要前往蟹堡王的厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We now take you live to the Krusty Krab's kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直播蟹黄堡制作实况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the main event
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.94,0:13:20.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝为接下来的任务进行准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:20.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob prepares himself for the task ahead
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.40,0:13:24.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他切菜的模样仿佛一位雕刻大师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:24.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's chopping the veggies like a master sculptor
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在测试面包的弹性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's testing the bun's elasticity
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.16,0:13:32.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在挑选
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:32.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's picking
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.79,0:13:35.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表面干燥变硬程度最低的肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:35.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a patty with the least amount of freezer burn
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1696,722)}冻肉饼
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看它多闪耀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at it sparkle
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.25,0:13:41.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始做蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:41.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The patty is in play
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.96,0:13:45.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重复一遍  开始做蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:45.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I repeat, the patty is in play
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.76,0:13:48.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这厨艺展示得属实优美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:48.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a fantastic display of fry cook skills
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.93,0:13:51.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能不能动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:51.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you hurry it up already?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.48,0:14:01.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝似乎有些分神了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:01.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob seems distracted
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出了一点小问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong, folks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.37,0:14:21.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,煎炸厨师起了某种疹子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:21.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fry cook has broken out in some kind of rash
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must fini--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,f--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.09,0:14:26.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做完
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:26.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,finish
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了  海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做的第千千万万亿个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My kazillionth Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.56,0:14:40.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚煎好  热乎着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:40.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hot off the grill
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我可吃不下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't consume this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.58,0:14:55.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这可怜的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:55.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You poor Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实在太不卫生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is so unsanitary
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这就走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm outta here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  别走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, don't go
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.47,0:15:16.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道你是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:16.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's goin' on with you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.18,0:15:18.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你坏了我的生意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:18.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you're ruinin' me business
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.03,0:15:30.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我做不了蟹黄堡  那我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:30.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I can't cook Krabby Patties, then who am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.61,0:15:33.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疹子太该死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:33.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Curse this blasted rash
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.58,0:15:35.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的疹子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:35.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My rash?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's gone
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.42,0:15:49.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:49.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I'm cured
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.13,0:15:54.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你样子感觉一点都没康复  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:54.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't look cured to me, son
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.01,0:15:58.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:58.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm cure--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.31,0:16:04.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:04.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm cure--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.81,0:16:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.15,0:16:13.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会想你的  蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:13.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna miss you, Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.99,0:16:17.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:17.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happening to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这还不明显
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.29,0:16:25.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你对蟹黄堡过敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:25.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're allergic to Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚收到的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This just in
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝对蟹黄堡过敏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob's allergic to Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对蟹黄堡过敏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allergic to Krabby Patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.17,0:16:34.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里有专治过敏的医生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:34.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is there an allergist in the house?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是过敏专科医师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm an allergist
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.97,0:16:37.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:37.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dibs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.14,0:16:42.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:42.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say Ah
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.48,0:16:43.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嚏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:43.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Choo
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过敏专科医师笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allergist humor
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由于长期暴露在蟹黄堡附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:51.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The constant exposure to Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.15,0:16:55.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,导致你产生了过敏性免疫反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:55.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has caused a hypersensitive immunological reaction
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say what now?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡会让你发痒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties make you itch
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.87,0:17:00.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:00.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能治好你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can cure you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.84,0:17:09.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝只是需要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:09.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob just needs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,与过敏原进行隔绝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to be isolated from the allergen
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是跟蟹黄堡进行隔绝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In this case, Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚好会帮他隔绝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I know just how to do it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.05,0:17:21.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽说我的旧潜水服有点笨重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:21.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My old divin' suit's a little bulky
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.77,0:17:23.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过可以保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:23.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it'll keep you safe
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把你跟四散的蟹黄堡颗粒隔开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from any stray patty particles
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.23,0:17:26.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:26.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碰碰运气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here goes nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.12,0:17:45.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:45.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it wonderful, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又能做蟹黄堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can cook Krabby Patties again
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoop-dee-diddly-doo
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  开做了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点点这个  一点点那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little bit of this, a little bit of that
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.39,0:17:59.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再一点这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:17:59.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some of this
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡  双倍腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:04.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty with double pickle
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.14,0:18:05.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不加海草酱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:05.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hold the kelp-sup
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.73,0:18:08.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:08.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.60,0:18:11.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两个蟹黄堡  再加一份珊瑚薯条卷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:11.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two patty singles with an order of curly coral bits
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就快掌握诀窍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gettin' the hang of it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.53,0:18:15.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:15.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.90,0:18:18.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:18.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不能就这样工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't work like this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.87,0:18:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,学会蹲下  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Learn to duck, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.78,0:18:23.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:23.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.74,0:18:24.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:24.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.75,0:18:26.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:26.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quittin' time
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.58,0:18:30.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:30.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才刚会用这套衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just when I was gettin' this suit figured out
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.97,0:18:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's goin' on in here, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.02,0:18:47.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我脱不掉这身衣服  回不了家了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:47.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take this suit off and I can't go home
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么办  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:49.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'll I do, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.06,0:18:53.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从今往后你只能睡厨房里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:53.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll have to bunk in the kitchen from now on
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在工作岗位过夜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Work sleepover
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.32,0:19:05.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早就想到你有可能会不方便回家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I figured you might have a little trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,getting back to your homestead
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我就带了点日用品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I brung along some supplies
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.21,0:19:12.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也忘不掉这个小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:12.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't forget this little feller
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:16.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,几天后
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.12,0:19:46.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:46.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.16,0:19:50.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人们也对蟹黄堡过敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:50.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the customers are allergic to patties too
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.38,0:19:57.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快  进潜水服里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:57.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, get inside the suit
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来会比较安全
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll be safe in here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.35,0:20:11.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的疹子消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:11.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My rash is gone
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.73,0:20:12.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:12.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Totally cured
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.90,0:20:17.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:17.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝失去理智了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob lost his marbles
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.36,0:20:24.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他把客人全吸进那个疯狂装置里了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:22.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He sucked all the customers
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,into that crazy contraption
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.87,0:20:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡过敏症在到处传染  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The patty allergy's spreading, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客人们也都过敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:29.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The customers are allergic too
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静点  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Calm down, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.41,0:20:33.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定是有些言过其
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:33.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're just exaggerat--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.50,0:20:36.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你别怕  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:36.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.67,0:20:37.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:37.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll save you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.80,0:20:41.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:41.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's better
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  快进衣服里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, get in the suit
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别让过敏给传染了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't let the allergy get you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.22,0:20:48.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:48.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.10,0:20:50.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不住进那个铁罐子里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:50.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not living in that tin can
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.85,0:20:53.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更何况你还在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:53.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,especially with you inside it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.73,0:20:58.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:58.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.94,0:21:00.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:00.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Before it's too late
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.74,0:21:05.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:05.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我过来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just checkin' in to see
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.92,0:21:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how y'all are doin'?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoo-doggy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.39,0:21:31.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里样子乱糟糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:31.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like a cattle drive came through here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.01,0:21:33.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:33.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all okay in there?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很有事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I am not
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.81,0:21:39.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这衣服臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:39.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This suit smells revolting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.48,0:21:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还好我有新买的古龙水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thing I have my new cologne
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.40,0:21:44.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,头足香料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:44.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cephalopod Spice
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.79,0:21:54.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们打喷嚏不是因为蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:54.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all weren't sneezin' from patties
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.29,0:21:57.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是对章鱼哥的便宜货古龙水过敏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:57.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're allergic to Squidward's cheap cologne
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.87,0:22:00.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要让你们知道我的清香型香水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:00.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have you know that my eau de toilette
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可贵了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is tres pricey
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.51,0:22:07.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,潜水服把过敏原集中在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:07.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The suit's concentrated the allergen
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.13,0:22:10.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们的疹子变严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:10.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all's rashes are goin' critical
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:17.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,很久以后
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.27,0:22:20.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:20.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.65,0:22:22.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会害人过敏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:22.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allergy-free
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.78,0:22:32.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我还有古龙水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.78,0:22:32.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least I still have my cologne
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.92,0:22:40.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:40.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
